OL,3,CMinisters have 'no plans' to force
OL,4,Cbusinesses to accept four-day week
OL,5,Cdemands
OL,7,FThe PA news agency understands any
OL,8,Fplan to open up "compressed hours" to
OL,9,Fmore workers would not result in bank
OL,10,Fholiday-style weekends each week, and
OL,11,Fthat employees would usually need to
OL,12,Fwork their contracted hours, even if
OL,13,Fthey choose to over fewer days.
OL,15,FThe Whitehall spokesperson said: "We
OL,16,Fhave no plans to impose a four-day
OL,17,Fworking week on employers or
OL,18,Femployees. Any changes to employment
OL,19,Flegislation will be consulted on,
OL,20,Fworking in partnership with business.
