OL,4,Cbusinesses to accept four-day week
OL,5,Cdemands
OL,7,F"We are working in close partnership
OL,8,Fwith business and civil society to
OL,9,Ffind the balance between improving
OL,10,Fworkers' rights while supporting the
OL,11,Fbrilliant businesses that pay people's
OL,12,Fwages."
OL,14,FThe Department for Business and Trade
OL,15,Fvowed to set out further details of
OL,16,Fits approach within 100 days.
OL,18,FLabour released a document titled
OL,19,FLabour's Plan To Make Work Pay two
OL,20,Fdays after Rishi Sunak called the
OL,21,FGeneral Election in May.
