OL,4,Cbusinesses to accept four-day week
OL,5,Cdemands
OL,7,F"Labour must listen to businesses who
OL,8,Fare petrified about day one employment
OL,9,Frights and bringing in the four-day
OL,10,Fweek through the back door."
OL,12,FA Labour source said "the
OL,13,FConservatives pledged to make flexible
OL,14,Fworking the default then failed to do
OL,15,Fso", a reference to the party's
OL,16,Fwinning 2019 manifesto which Boris
OL,17,FJohnson fronted, which read: "We will
OL,18,Fencourage flexible working and consult
OL,19,Fon making it the default unless
OL,20,Femployers have good reasons not to."
